{
  "text": "Finally, the results for the job-performance dataset show only a small change in effect on down-weighting outliers, as found by [CITATION_1] . As in their analysis, study 56 has been down-weighted (to 10% here), but study 8, which they also removed, was hardly down-weighted. Overall, this methodology agrees well with previous work on outliers.",
  "citation_candidates": [
